<span id="freeTextContainer8716116000894518743">THE SNOW LEOPARD was a book I nearly didn&apos;t finish. It does get trying in some parts. This is one of the few books that I actually had a dream about while reading it. It seemed profound at the time, and I was very glad that I soldiered on to the end of Matthiessen&apos;s wonderful story.</span>
  <span id="freeText8716116000894518743" style="display:none">THE SNOW LEOPARD was a book I nearly didn't finish. It does get trying in some parts. This is one of the few books that I actually had a dream about while reading it. It seemed profound at the time, and I was very glad that I soldiered on to the end of Matthiessen's wonderful story.</span>
