          <div><span class="uitext greyText">Recommends it for: </span>
           <span class="uitext reviewText">everyone who like travel stories with a deeper background</span></div>

        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7408130-sylvia?shelf=read-2012">read-2012</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7408130-sylvia?shelf=challenge-2012">challenge-2012</a>
